{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"Several years ago here at TED, Peter Skillman"},{"time":3000,"text":"introduced a design challenge"},{"time":5000,"text":"called the marshmallow challenge."},{"time":7000,"text":"And the idea's pretty simple:"},{"time":9000,"text":"Teams of four have to build the tallest free-standing structure"},{"time":11000,"text":"out of 20 sticks of spaghetti,"},{"time":13000,"text":"one yard of tape, one yard of string"},{"time":15000,"text":"and a marshmallow."},{"time":17000,"text":"The marshmallow has to be on top."},{"time":19000,"text":"And, though it seems really simple, it's actually pretty hard"},{"time":22000,"text":"because it forces people"},{"time":24000,"text":"to collaborate very quickly."},{"time":26000,"text":"And so, I thought this was an interesting idea,"},{"time":28000,"text":"and I incorporated it into a design workshop."},{"time":31000,"text":"And it was a huge success."},{"time":33000,"text":"And since then, I've conducted"},{"time":35000,"text":"about 70 design workshops across the world"},{"time":37000,"text":"with students and designers and architects,"},{"time":39000,"text":"even the CTOs of the Fortune 50,"},{"time":42000,"text":"and there's something about this exercise"},{"time":44000,"text":"that reveals very deep lessons"},{"time":46000,"text":"about the nature of collaboration,"},{"time":48000,"text":"and I'd like to share some of them with you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":50000,"text":"So, normally, most people begin"},{"time":53000,"text":"by orienting themselves to the task."},{"time":56000,"text":"They talk about it, they figure out what it's going to look like,"},{"time":59000,"text":"they jockey for power."},{"time":61000,"text":"Then they spend some time planning, organizing,"},{"time":63000,"text":"they sketch and they lay out spaghetti."},{"time":66000,"text":"They spend the majority of their time"},{"time":68000,"text":"assembling the sticks into ever-growing structures."},{"time":71000,"text":"And then finally, just as they're running out of time,"},{"time":74000,"text":"someone takes out the marshmallow,"},{"time":76000,"text":"and then they gingerly put it on top,"},{"time":79000,"text":"and then they stand back, and -- ta-da! --"},{"time":82000,"text":"they admire their work."},{"time":84000,"text":"But what really happens, most of the time,"},{"time":86000,"text":"is that the \"ta-da\" turns into an \"uh-oh,\""},{"time":89000,"text":"because the weight of the marshmallow causes the entire structure"},{"time":91000,"text":"to buckle and to collapse."}]},{"cues":[{"time":93000,"text":"So there are a number of people"},{"time":95000,"text":"who have a lot more \"uh-oh\" moments than others,"},{"time":98000,"text":"and among the worst are recent graduates of business school."},{"time":101000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":104000,"text":"They lie, they cheat, they get distracted"},{"time":107000,"text":"and they produce really lame structures."},{"time":109000,"text":"And of course there are teams"},{"time":111000,"text":"that have a lot more \"ta-da\" structures,"},{"time":113000,"text":"and among the best are recent graduates of kindergarten."},{"time":116000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":118000,"text":"And it's pretty amazing."},{"time":120000,"text":"As Peter tells us,"},{"time":122000,"text":"not only do they produce the tallest structures,"},{"time":124000,"text":"but they're the most interesting structures of them all."}]},{"cues":[{"time":127000,"text":"So the question you want to ask is:"},{"time":129000,"text":"How come? Why? What is it about them?"},{"time":131000,"text":"And Peter likes to say that"},{"time":133000,"text":"none of the kids spend any time"},{"time":135000,"text":"trying to be CEO of Spaghetti, Inc. Right?"},{"time":138000,"text":"They don't spend time jockeying for power."},{"time":140000,"text":"But there's another reason as well."},{"time":142000,"text":"And the reason is that business students are trained"},{"time":144000,"text":"to find the single right plan, right?"},{"time":147000,"text":"And then they execute on it."},{"time":149000,"text":"And then what happens is, when they put the marshmallow on the top,"},{"time":151000,"text":"they run out of time and what happens?"},{"time":153000,"text":"It's a crisis."},{"time":155000,"text":"Sound familiar? Right."},{"time":158000,"text":"What kindergarteners do differently"},{"time":160000,"text":"is that they start with the marshmallow,"},{"time":162000,"text":"and they build prototypes, successive prototypes,"},{"time":165000,"text":"always keeping the marshmallow on top,"},{"time":167000,"text":"so they have multiple times to fix when they build prototypes along the way."},{"time":170000,"text":"Designers recognize this type of collaboration"},{"time":173000,"text":"as the essence of the iterative process."},{"time":176000,"text":"And with each version, kids get instant feedback"},{"time":178000,"text":"about what works and what doesn't work."}]},{"cues":[{"time":181000,"text":"So the capacity to play in prototype is really essential,"},{"time":184000,"text":"but let's look at how different teams perform."},{"time":187000,"text":"So the average for most people is around 20 inches;"},{"time":190000,"text":"business schools students, about half of that;"},{"time":192000,"text":"lawyers, a little better, but not much better than that,"},{"time":195000,"text":"kindergarteners, better than most adults."},{"time":197000,"text":"Who does the very best?"},{"time":199000,"text":"Architects and engineers, thankfully."},{"time":202000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":207000,"text":"Thirty-nine inches is the tallest structure I've seen."},{"time":210000,"text":"And why is it? Because they understand triangles"},{"time":213000,"text":"and self-reinforcing geometrical patterns"},{"time":215000,"text":"are the key to building"},{"time":217000,"text":"stable structures."},{"time":219000,"text":"So CEOs, a little bit better than average,"},{"time":222000,"text":"but here's where it gets interesting."},{"time":224000,"text":"If you put you put an executive admin. on the team,"},{"time":226000,"text":"they get significantly better."},{"time":228000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":231000,"text":"It's incredible. You know, you look around, you go, \"Oh, that team's going to win.\""},{"time":233000,"text":"You can just tell beforehand. And why is that?"},{"time":235000,"text":"Because they have special skills"},{"time":237000,"text":"of facilitation."},{"time":239000,"text":"They manage the process, they understand the process."},{"time":241000,"text":"And any team who manages"},{"time":243000,"text":"and pays close attention to work"},{"time":246000,"text":"will significantly improve the team's performance."},{"time":249000,"text":"Specialized skills and facilitation skills"},{"time":252000,"text":"are the combination that leads to strong success."},{"time":255000,"text":"If you have 10 teams that typically perform,"},{"time":257000,"text":"you'll get maybe six or so that have standing structures."}]},{"cues":[{"time":259000,"text":"And I tried something interesting."},{"time":261000,"text":"I thought, let's up the ante, once."},{"time":264000,"text":"So I offered a 10,000 dollar prize of software to the winning team."},{"time":267000,"text":"So what do you think happened to these design students?"},{"time":270000,"text":"What was the result?"},{"time":273000,"text":"Here's what happened:"},{"time":275000,"text":"Not one team had a standing structure."},{"time":279000,"text":"If anyone had built, say, a one inch structure,"},{"time":282000,"text":"they would have taken home the prize."},{"time":284000,"text":"So, isn't that interesting? That high stakes"},{"time":286000,"text":"have a strong impact."},{"time":288000,"text":"We did the exercise again with the same students."},{"time":290000,"text":"What do you think happened then?"},{"time":292000,"text":"So now they understand the value of prototyping."},{"time":298000,"text":"So the same team went from being the very worst"},{"time":300000,"text":"to being among the very best."},{"time":302000,"text":"They produced the tallest structures in the least amount of time."},{"time":305000,"text":"So there's deep lessons for us"},{"time":307000,"text":"about the nature of incentives and success."}]},{"cues":[{"time":310000,"text":"So, you might ask: Why would anyone"},{"time":312000,"text":"actually spend time writing a marshmallow challenge?"},{"time":315000,"text":"And the reason is, I help create"},{"time":317000,"text":"digital tools and processes"},{"time":319000,"text":"to help teams build cars and video games"},{"time":321000,"text":"and visual effects."},{"time":323000,"text":"And what the marshmallow challenge does"},{"time":325000,"text":"is it helps them identify the hidden assumptions."},{"time":328000,"text":"Because, frankly,"},{"time":330000,"text":"every project has its own marshmallow, doesn't it?"},{"time":333000,"text":"The challenge provides a shared experience,"},{"time":335000,"text":"a common language,"},{"time":337000,"text":"a common stance to build the right prototype."},{"time":339000,"text":"And so, this is the value of the experience,"},{"time":341000,"text":"of this so simple exercise."}]},{"cues":[{"time":343000,"text":"And those of you who are interested"},{"time":345000,"text":"may want to go to MarshmallowChallenge.com."},{"time":347000,"text":"It's a blog that you can look at"},{"time":349000,"text":"how to build the marshmallows."},{"time":351000,"text":"There's step-by-step instructions on this."},{"time":353000,"text":"There are crazy examples from around the world"},{"time":356000,"text":"of how people tweak and adjust the system."},{"time":358000,"text":"There's world records that are on this as well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":360000,"text":"And the fundamental lesson, I believe,"},{"time":362000,"text":"is that design truly is"},{"time":364000,"text":"a contact sport."},{"time":366000,"text":"It demands that we bring all of our senses to the task,"},{"time":369000,"text":"and that we apply the very best of our thinking,"},{"time":371000,"text":"our feeling and our doing"},{"time":374000,"text":"to the challenge that we have at hand."},{"time":376000,"text":"And sometimes, a little prototype of this experience"},{"time":379000,"text":"is all that it takes to turn us"},{"time":381000,"text":"from an \"uh-oh\" moment to a \"ta-da\" moment."},{"time":383000,"text":"And that can make a big difference."}]},{"cues":[{"time":385000,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":387000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}